EMS Version 2 Update/ Improvement
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

(1) All dates, should be in Indian format i.e., dd/mm/yyyy
(2) If I edit an Invoice, and (say) I changed the currency from USD to EURO, it always shows the new invoice with USD.
(3) For Received Invoice, the Autosuggest does not work for fields like - Description of Service, SAC/HSN etc.
(4) In Received Invoice, currency does not work correctly.
(5) In Received Invoice, Price & Tax calculation does not work, when Price is in Decimal.
(6) We cannot edit Received Invoice
